snippet.title: Dead Man's Phone Season 1 Trailer | Android Store | 2021
snippet.description:
FULL RELEASE 2021

You are a New Scotland Yard detective who investigates and solves murders through the smartphone of victims.

Search through a victims phone. See their personal messages, photos, apps. Find clues, interrogate suspects – decide how the narrative unfolds.
